{
  "chapter": "065",
  "title": "孙子吴起列传",
  "translations": {
    "1": {
      "title": "孙武练兵",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：孙武\">孙子（孙武）</span>名武，是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>人。他以<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">兵法</span>谒见<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：姬阖庐\">王阖庐（姬阖庐）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：姬阖庐\">阖庐（姬阖庐）</span>说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>写的<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">十三篇</span>，我都看过了，可以用来小试一下操练军队吗？\"回答说：\"可以。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：姬阖庐\">阖庐（姬阖庐）</span>说：\"可以试用<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">妇人</span>吗？\"回答说：\"可以。\"于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：姬阖庐\">阖庐（姬阖庐）</span>答应了，从宫中找出美<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">女</span>，选得<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">百八十人</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：孙武\">孙子（孙武）</span>把她们分为二队，用王的宠姬<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二人</span>各为队长，都让她们持<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">戟</span>。命令她们说：\"你们知道自己的心以及左右手和背吗？\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">妇人</span>说：\"知道。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：孙武\">孙子（孙武）</span>说：\"向前，就看心；向左，看左手；向右，看右手；向后，就看背。\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">妇人</span>说：\"是。\"军法既已公布，于是设置<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">鈇钺</span>，<span class=\"idiom\" title=\"成语\">三令五申</span>。然后击鼓令她们向右，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">妇人</span>大笑。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：孙武\">孙子（孙武）</span>说：\"军法不明确，号令不熟悉，是将领的过错。\"再次三令五申，击鼓令她们向左，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">妇人</span>又大笑。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：孙武\">孙子（孙武）</span>说：\"军法不明，号令不熟，是将领的过错；既已明白而不执行军法，就是军吏<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>兵的过错。\"便要<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">斩</span>左右两队队长。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>王在台上观看，见将要<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">斩</span>自己的爱姬，大为惊骇。急忙派使者下令说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">寡人</span>已经知道<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将军</span>能用兵了。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">寡人</span>没有这两位爱姬，就食不甘味，望不要<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">斩</span>她们。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：孙武\">孙子（孙武）</span>说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>已经受命为将，将在军中，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>命有所不受。\"于是<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">斩</span>队长<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二人</span>以示众。起用次位者为队长，再击鼓令之。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">妇人</span>们左右前后跪起都合乎<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">规矩</span>绳墨，无人敢出声。于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：孙武\">孙子（孙武）</span>派使者报告吴王说：\"兵已整齐，王可试着下来观看，随王的意愿使用她们，即使赴汤蹈火也可。\"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">吴</span>王说：\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将军</span>请解散回舍休息，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">寡人</span>不愿下观。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：孙武\">孙子（孙武）</span>说：\"王只是喜好言谈，不能使用实战。\"于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：姬阖庐\">阖庐（姬阖庐）</span>知道<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：孙武\">孙子（孙武）</span>能用兵，最后任命他为将。向西<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span>强大的<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国，攻入<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">郢</span>都，向北威震<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋</span>，显名于<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>之间，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：孙武\">孙子（孙武）</span>也是有功的。"
    },
    "2": {
      "title": "孙膑受刑",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孙武</span>死后，过了<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">百多年（时长）</span>有<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孙膑</span>出世。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：孙膑\">膑（孙膑）</span>生于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">阿</span>、鄄之间，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：孙膑\">膑（孙膑）</span>也是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孙武</span>的后世<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子孙</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孙膑</span>曾经与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">庞涓</span>一同学习<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">兵法</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">庞涓</span>侍奉<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>之后，得以成为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏惠王\">惠王（魏惠王）</span>的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将军</span>，自以为才能不及<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孙膑</span>，便暗中派人召来<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孙膑</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：孙膑\">膑（孙膑）</span>到后，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">庞涓</span>担心他比自己贤能，嫉恨他，就用法令<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">刑</span>断他的两足并<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">黥</span>其面，想让他隐藏起来不得露面。"
    },
    "3": {
      "title": "赛马献策",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>使者来到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孙膑</span>以<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">刑</span>徒身份暗中去见，游说<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>使。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>使认为他奇异，偷偷把他载到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>国。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>将<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田忌</span>赏识他而以客礼相待。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：田忌\">忌（田忌）</span>多次与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>的诸<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">公子</span>赛马重金下注。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：孙膑\">孙子（孙膑）</span>看他们的<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">马</span>脚力相差不远，而<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">马</span>有上、中、下三等。于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：孙膑\">孙子（孙膑）</span>对<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田忌</span>说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>尽管加大赌注，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>能让<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>获胜。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田忌</span>相信他，于是与王以及诸<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">公子</span>赛马赌<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">千金</span>。到临比赛时，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：孙膑\">孙子（孙膑）</span>说：\"如今用<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>的下等马对他们的上等马，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">取</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>的上等马对他们的中等马，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">取</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>的中等马对他们的下等马。\"三轮赛马完毕后，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田忌</span>一败两胜，终于赢得王的<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">千金</span>。于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：田忌\">忌（田忌）</span>把<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：孙膑\">孙子（孙膑）</span>进荐给<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：齐威王\">威王（齐威王）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：齐威王\">威王（齐威王）</span>向他请教<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">兵法</span>，就任他为军师。"
    },
    "4": {
      "title": "桂陵之战",
      "text": "此后<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>急迫，向<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>求救。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">齐威王</span>想任<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孙膑</span>为将，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：孙膑\">膑（孙膑）</span>推辞说：\"受过<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">刑</span>的人不合适。\"于是便任命<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田忌</span>为将，而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：孙膑\">孙子（孙膑）</span>为军师，坐在<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">辎车</span>中，坐着出谋划策。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田忌</span>想要率兵直接去<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>国，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：孙膑\">孙子（孙膑）</span>说：\"要解开杂乱纠缠的丝线，不能挥拳乱打；劝架的人，不能参与厮打，击其要害捣其虚空，形势格禁，则双方自然解开。如今<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>相<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>的轻兵锐卒必已耗尽在外，老弱疲惫留守在内。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>不如率兵疾驰<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">大梁</span>，占据其街道要路，冲其空虚，他必放弃<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>而自救。这样我们一举就可以解<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>之<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">围</span>而又在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>军疲敝时取胜。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田忌</span>听从他，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>军果然离开<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">邯郸</span>，与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>军在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">桂陵</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">战</span>，大<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">梁</span>军。"
    },
    "5": {
      "title": "马陵之战",
      "text": "过了<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">十三年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>向<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>告急。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田忌</span>率兵前往，直奔<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">大梁</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>将<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">庞涓</span>听说了，就离开<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>而回援，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>军已经越过边界向西进军了。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：孙膑\">孙子（孙膑）</span>对<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">田忌</span>说：\"那三<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋</span>之兵素来悍勇而轻视<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>向来号称怯懦，善于<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">战</span>的人应顺势加以利导。<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">兵法</span>，<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">百里</span>赶利者要损折<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">上将</span>，<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">五十里</span>赶利者军队只能半数抵达。让<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>军进入<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>地后设<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">十万灶</span>，<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">第二天</span>设<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">五万灶</span>，再<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">第二天</span>设<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三万灶</span>。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">庞涓</span>行军<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">三天</span>，大喜说：\"我本来就知道<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>军怯懦，进入我国境内才<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">三天</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>卒逃亡者已过半。\"于是舍弃步兵，率其轻锐昼夜兼程追击。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：孙膑\">孙子（孙膑）</span>估算他的行程，傍晚应当到达<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">马陵</span>。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">马陵</span>道路狭窄，两旁多险隘，可以埋伏兵马，于是砍下大树削白树干，在上面写：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">庞涓</span>死在此树之下\"。又命令<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>军善射者<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">万弩</span>，夹道埋伏，约定：\"傍晚见到火举起就一齐发射。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">庞涓</span>果然在夜间到砍伐的大树下，看见白书，便点火照看。还没读完，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>军<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">万弩</span>齐发，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>军大乱相失。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">庞涓</span>自知智穷兵<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">败</span>，就自<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">刭</span>，说：\"终究成就这<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">竖子</span>的名声！\"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>军乘胜尽<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span>其军，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">虏</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏太子申\">申（魏太子申）</span>而还。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孙膑</span>因此名显天下，世间流传他的<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">兵法</span>。"
    },
    "6": {
      "title": "吴起事鲁",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吴起</span>是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">卫</span>人，喜好用兵。曾师从<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">曾子</span>学习，侍奉<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">鲁</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>人<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">鲁</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">鲁</span>想任<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吴起</span>为将，但<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吴起</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">取</span>了<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">女</span>为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">妻</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">鲁</span>国因此对他猜疑。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吴起</span>于是想要成名，便<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>了自己的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">妻</span>子，以表明不附<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>国。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">鲁</span>终于任命他为将。他率军<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>，大<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span>齐军。"
    },
    "7": {
      "title": "遭谗去鲁",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">鲁</span>国有人毁谤<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吴起</span>说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：吴起\">起（吴起）</span>为人，是猜忌残忍的人。他年少时，家中积蓄<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">千金</span>，游说求仕没有成功，家道因而<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span>败，乡里人嘲笑他，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吴起</span>便<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>死诽谤自己的<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三十馀人</span>，然后向东出<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">卫</span>国的城门。他与自己的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">母</span>亲诀别，咬破手臂发誓说：<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：吴起\">起（吴起）</span>不做到<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">卿相</span>，决不再回<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">卫</span>国。于是去侍奉<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">曾子</span>。居住了一段时间，他的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">母</span>亲死了，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：吴起\">起（吴起）</span>最终没有回去。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">曾子</span>因此轻视他，与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：吴起\">起（吴起）</span>绝交。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：吴起\">起（吴起）</span>便到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">鲁</span>国，学<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">兵法</span>以侍奉<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">鲁</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">鲁</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>猜疑他，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：吴起\">起（吴起）</span>就<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">妻</span>以求为将。那<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">鲁</span>是小国，有<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">战</span>胜之名，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>就会图谋<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">鲁</span>国了。而且<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">鲁</span>与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">卫</span>是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">兄弟</span>之国，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>任用<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：吴起\">起（吴起）</span>，就是放弃<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">卫</span>国。\"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">鲁</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>猜疑他，辞退了<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吴起</span>。"
    },
    "8": {
      "title": "起相魏国",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吴起</span>于是听说<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏文侯\">文侯（魏文侯）</span>贤明，想要侍奉他。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏文侯\">文侯（魏文侯）</span>问<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李克</span>：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吴起</span>是什么样的人？\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李克</span>说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：吴起\">起（吴起）</span>贪心而好色，但用兵连<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">司马穰苴</span>都不能超过。\"于是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>文侯任命他为将，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">拔</span>取<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">五城</span>。"
    },
    "9": {
      "title": "吮疽得士",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：吴起\">起（吴起）</span>做将军时，与最下等的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>卒同衣同食。睡眠不设<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">席</span>，行军不骑乘，亲自背负自己的粮食，与<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>卒同分劳苦。有<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>卒生毒疮，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：吴起\">起（吴起）</span>为他吮吸脓液。这<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>卒的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">母</span>亲听说后哭起来。有人问：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>只是个士卒，而将军亲自为他吮吸脓疮，你为什么要哭呢？\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">母</span>亲说：\"不是这样的。往年吴公曾为他的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">父</span>亲吮疮，他的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">父</span>亲<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">战</span>斗时头不回顾，于是死在敌人手里。吴公如今又为他的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>吮疮，我不知道他要死在哪里了。所以哭啊。\""
    },
    "10": {
      "title": "任西河守",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏文侯\">文侯（魏文侯）</span>因<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吴起</span>善于用兵、廉洁公平、能完全得到<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>卒的心，便任命他为<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">西河</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">守</span>，以抵御<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>。"
    },
    "11": {
      "title": "论德与险",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏文侯\">文侯（魏文侯）</span>死后，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：吴起\">起（吴起）</span>侍奉他的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏武侯\">武侯（魏武侯）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏武侯\">武侯（魏武侯）</span>在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">西河</span>浮舟而下，到中流时，回头对<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吴起</span>说：\"真美啊这山河的险固，这是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>国的瑰宝！\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：吴起\">起（吴起）</span>回答说：\"<span class=\"idiom\" title=\"成语\">在德不在险</span>。从前<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">三苗</span>氏左临<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">洞庭</span>，右靠<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">彭蠡</span>，不修<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">德</span><span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">义</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">禹</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">灭</span>了他们。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">夏</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">桀</span>的居地，左有<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">河济</span>，右有<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">泰华</span>，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">伊阙</span>在其南，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">羊肠</span>在其北，修<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">政</span>不<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">仁</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汤</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">放</span>逐了他。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">殷</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">纣</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">之国</span>，左有<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">孟门</span>，右有<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">太行</span>，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">常山</span>在其北，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">大河</span>经其南，修<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">政</span>不<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">德</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武王</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>了他。由此看来，<span class=\"idiom\" title=\"成语\">在德不在险</span>。若<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>不修<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">德</span>，<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">舟</span>中之人全都会成为敌国之人。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏武侯\">武侯（魏武侯）</span>说：\"说得好。\""
    },
    "12": {
      "title": "不如田文",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吴起</span>做<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">西河</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">守</span>，名声很大。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>国设置相位，任用<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏相田文\">田文（魏相田文）</span>为相。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吴起</span>不高兴，对<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏相田文\">田文（魏相田文）</span>说：\"请让我与<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>论功，可以吗？\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏相田文\">田文（魏相田文）</span>说：\"可以。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：吴起\">起（吴起）</span>说：\"统领<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">三军</span>，使<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>卒乐于赴死，敌国不敢图谋，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>和<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：吴起\">起（吴起）</span>谁胜？\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏相田文\">文（魏相田文）</span>说：\"不如<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：吴起\">起（吴起）</span>说：\"治理<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">百官</span>，亲近<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">万民</span>，充实<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">府库</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>和<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：吴起\">起（吴起）</span>谁胜？\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏相田文\">文（魏相田文）</span>说：\"不如<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：吴起\">起（吴起）</span>说：\"镇守<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">西河</span>使<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>兵不敢东进，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>宾服听从，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>和<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：吴起\">起（吴起）</span>谁胜？\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏相田文\">文（魏相田文）</span>说：\"不如<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：吴起\">起（吴起）</span>说：\"这三方面，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>都在我之下，而位在我之上，为什么？\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏相田文\">文（魏相田文）</span>说：\"主少国疑，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大臣</span>未归附，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">百姓</span>不信服，当此时，把相位托付给<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>呢？还是托付给我呢？\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：吴起\">起（吴起）</span>默然良久，说：\"托付给<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏相田文\">文（魏相田文）</span>说：\"这就是我居于<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>之上的原因。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吴起</span>才自知不如<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏相田文\">田文（魏相田文）</span>。"
    },
    "13": {
      "title": "被谗入楚",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏相田文\">田文（魏相田文）</span>死后，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：公叔座\">公叔（公叔座）</span>为相，娶了<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>国的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">公主</span>，而嫉害<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吴起</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：公叔座\">公叔（公叔座）</span>的仆人说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：吴起\">起（吴起）</span>容易被驱除。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：公叔座\">公叔（公叔座）</span>说：\"怎么办？\"那仆人说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吴起</span>为人节俭廉直且爱好名声。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>可先对<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏武侯\">武侯（魏武侯）</span>说：<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吴起</span>是贤人，但您的国家小，又与强<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>接壤，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>私下里担心<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：吴起\">起（吴起）</span>没有留在我国的心意。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏武侯\">武侯（魏武侯）</span>将会说：怎么办？<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>便对<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏武侯\">武侯（魏武侯）</span>说：请试着用<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">公主</span>款待他，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：吴起\">起（吴起）</span>如果有留心就必定接受。没有留心就必定推辞。以此占卜他。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>再召<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吴起</span>同归家中，让<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">公主</span>发怒而轻慢<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吴起</span>见<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">公主</span>轻慢<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>，必定推辞。\"于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吴起</span>见<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">公主</span>轻慢<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>相，果然推辞了<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏武侯\">武侯（魏武侯）</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏武侯\">武侯（魏武侯）</span>因此对他产生怀疑而不再信任。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吴起</span>害怕获罪，就离开，前往<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国。"
    },
    "14": {
      "title": "变法惨死",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：楚悼王\">悼王（楚悼王）</span>一向听说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：吴起\">起（吴起）</span>贤能，一到就任命为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>相。他申明<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">法</span>度、审定政令，削减不急需的官位，废除<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">公族</span>中关系疏远者，用以抚养<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">战</span>斗的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>卒。要点在于强兵，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span>除合纵连横游说之言。于是南<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">平</span>百<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">越</span>；北<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">并</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">陈</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">蔡</span>，击退三<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋</span>；西<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>担忧<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国强盛。所以<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国的贵戚都想加害<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吴起</span>。等到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：楚悼王\">悼王（楚悼王）</span>去世，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">宗室</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大臣</span>作乱而<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>击<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吴起</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吴起</span>跑到王的尸体旁伏在上面。<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：吴起\">起（吴起）</span>的人因此<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">射</span>中并<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">刺</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吴起</span>，箭也一并射中<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：楚悼王\">悼王（楚悼王）</span>的尸体。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：楚悼王\">悼王（楚悼王）</span>安葬后，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>即位，便命<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">令尹</span>尽<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">射</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吴起</span>而同时射中王尸的人。因<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">射</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：吴起\">起（吴起）</span>事件被<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">夷宗</span>处死的有<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">七十馀家</span>。"
    },
    "15": {
      "title": "太史公曰",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太史公</span>说：世俗所称道的兵家，都称引<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：孙武\">孙子（孙武）</span>的<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">十三篇</span>和<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吴起</span>的<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">兵法</span>，世上多有流传，所以不再论述，只论述他们的行事所施为。俗语说：\"能做的不一定能说，能说的不一定能做。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：孙膑\">孙子（孙膑）</span>筹划<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">庞涓</span>显得高明了，然而却不能及早救自己免受<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">刑</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吴起</span>向<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏武侯\">武侯（魏武侯）</span>进说形势不如<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">德</span>政，然而施行于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>时，却因苛刻暴虐寡<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">恩</span>而丧身。可悲啊！"
    },
    "16": {
      "title": "赞",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：孙武\">孙子（孙武）</span>的<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">兵法</span>，一篇<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">十三篇</span>。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">美人</span>被<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">斩</span>，良<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将</span>由此得。孙膑被砍脚，筹划<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">庞涓</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吴起</span>相<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>，守<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">西河</span>被称贤；严酷事<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>，死后留权。"
    }
  }
}